    General layout & heading
    
    Section title: left-aligned large heading: FEATURED (bold) followed by CATEGORIES (regular). Use a modern sans-serif style, large uppercase for “FEATURED”.
    
    On the right of the heading show a two-option toggle (tabs) labeled Men and Women. Tab styles: pill shape with rounded border, selected tab dark with white text, unselected white background with dark text.
    
    Below the heading show a horizontal carousel/slider of category cards with pagination dots centered below the cards and left/right navigation arrows on the right side of the slider.
    
    Card design (per slide)
    
    Rounded corners (12–16px) and subtle shadow.
    
    Pastel background color per card (editable in theme editor).
    
